{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/gamedev/battleship","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A Python implementation of the classic battleship game.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.8953488372093024;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/b97f6/battleship-name-slaget.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.760736196319016%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Translating ships\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/a6d36/battleship-name-slaget.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/222b7/battleship-name-slaget.png 163w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/ff46a/battleship-name-slaget.png 325w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/a6d36/battleship-name-slaget.png 650w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/b97f6/battleship-name-slaget.png 958w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I decided to be very original with so common name as battleship. I know that Google Translate has about 40 different languages to choose from. I type in \"battle ship\" in English and start peeking different languages on the opposite side and I start tasting how these new words sound like.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.5673076923076923;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/b97f6/battleship-name-bato-yo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.80368098159509%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Translating ships\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/a6d36/battleship-name-bato-yo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/222b7/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 163w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/ff46a/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 325w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/a6d36/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 650w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/b97f6/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 958w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>So \"the ships, the battle\" = \"bato yo slaget\". You read it as <strong>BA</strong>rcelona <strong>TO</strong>rtuga <strong>YO</strong>lk <strong>SLA</strong>ck fri<strong>GATE</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.1013513513513513;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a016c/battleship_main_menu.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.79754601226993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Main menu\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a6d36/battleship_main_menu.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/222b7/battleship_main_menu.png 163w,\n/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/ff46a/battleship_main_menu.png 325w,\n/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a6d36/battleship_main_menu.png 650w,\n/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a016c/battleship_main_menu.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"history\" style=\"position:relative;\">History<a href=\"#history\" aria-label=\"history permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Basic logic adopted from <strong>@JBKahn</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/JBKahn/Battleship\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">code</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.0794701986754967;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/6bfd0/battleship_console.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.63803680981594%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Console version\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/a6d36/battleship_console.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/222b7/battleship_console.png 163w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/ff46a/battleship_console.png 325w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/a6d36/battleship_console.png 650w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/e548f/battleship_console.png 975w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/6bfd0/battleship_console.png 1011w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Features I liked:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>board size is a variable</li>\n<li>amount of players defined at runtime</li>\n<li>user ships can be placed on the board randomly</li>\n<li>simple console output</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.1013513513513513;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a016c/battleship_positioning.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.79754601226993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Positioning\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a6d36/battleship_positioning.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/222b7/battleship_positioning.png 163w,\n/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/ff46a/battleship_positioning.png 325w,\n/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a6d36/battleship_positioning.png 650w,\n/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a016c/battleship_positioning.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Important things added:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ships can not intersect</li>\n<li>unlimited amount of players (strange feature of course)</li>\n<li>split the monolith code onto small classes (one class - one file)</li>\n<li>game logic in separate python modules</li>\n</ul>\n<p>From <strong>@tmac-balla</strong> I've taken <a href=\"https://github.com/tmac-balla/battleship-game\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">the engine</a> that uses PyGame library and</p>\n<ul>\n<li>extended logic classes with sprites and fonts</li>\n<li>linked game classes to the engine</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"current-state-of-development\" style=\"position:relative;\">Current state of development<a href=\"#current-state-of-development\" aria-label=\"current state of development permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.1013513513513513;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a016c/battleship_gameplay.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.79754601226993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gameplay\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a6d36/battleship_gameplay.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/222b7/battleship_gameplay.png 163w,\n/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/ff46a/battleship_gameplay.png 325w,\n/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a6d36/battleship_gameplay.png 650w,\n/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a016c/battleship_gameplay.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>game ends when the game ends (just restart the app)</li>\n<li>not stable (auto ship positioning going wild)</li>\n<li>and maybe more...</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mikolasan/bato-yo-slaget\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"roadmap\" style=\"position:relative;\">Roadmap<a href=\"#roadmap\" aria-label=\"roadmap permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>OK, how to make a regular dead simple Battleship implementation to be more like <strong>Not your father's battleship</strong>?</p>\n<h3 id=\"gameplay-ideas\" style=\"position:relative;\">Gameplay ideas<a href=\"#gameplay-ideas\" aria-label=\"gameplay ideas permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Not square field (check out <a href=\"http://boardgamegeek.com/thread/605234/bravo-battleship\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this review</a> and read more about <a href=\"http://www.redblobgames.com/grids/hexagons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">hexagons</a>)</li>\n<li>Restoring fog of war plus moving ships</li>\n<li>Ships against coastal defense</li>\n<li>Aircraft carrier (5 cells) - relatively easy to find and sink, but it gives exploration data with some chance to locate one cell ships</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"technical-ideas\" style=\"position:relative;\">Technical ideas<a href=\"#technical-ideas\" aria-label=\"technical ideas permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Run Python on Android</li>\n<li>Switch to voxel engine</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.1013513513513513;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/a016c/battleship_win_message.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.79754601226993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"